During 7yrs with the ICO, I really got to know myself and where my strength and weaknesses were but now I know that I sleep around with other girls in the house while my wife is outside!

I am 29 years old and I want my wife who is 26, to get pregnant ASAP. Whenever we don’t go out, my wife gets jealous.

I had an arrangement with a rich sugar mummy. I brought her pictures of a lady who is younger than I am. She thought that was my 21yr old gf but newsflash! She is no longer sweet in bed like before.

My aunt reminds me a lot of my former lover who died during the Ebola crisis in Guinea Conakry in 2014. They look very si-ilar in every way possible, so much, that I can’t even stop thinking of my partner. I can’t bring myself to make love to my husband. With every attack of my libido, I just imagine my late woman and her lovely ways. I hate my aunt and wish she dies!
